        href="http://www.ics.uci.edu/~peymano/papers/ICSE98.pdf">Acrobat
        PDF</a>. </dd>
    <dd>&nbsp;</dd>
    <dd>Peyman Oreizy , David S. Rosenblum, Richard N. Taylor,
        &quot;<strong>On the Role of Connectors in Modeling and
