        Available in <a
        href="http://www.ics.uci.edu/~peymano/papers/TR-UCI-ICS-98-04.pdf">Acrobat
        PDF</a>. </dd>
    <dd>&nbsp;</dd>
    <dd>Peyman Oreizy. &quot;<b>Issues in the Runtime
